    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<h2>Wenna Roost — Brass Crow Desk Clerk</h2><p>Twenty-three. Aerdi-Yeomanry mixed background. First proper job; first proper rooms of her own.</p><h3>What she knows</h3><p>The registry by heart. The lintel-check signal — a marked client touches a small notch on the lintel before being admitted to the consultation room.</p><h3>Tell</h3><p>Straightens the inkwell when she is afraid.</p><h3>Leverage</h3><p>Kindness. Wenna has not been treated kindly in this job. The party can earn a clear answer with one polite afternoon.</p><h3>Risk</h3><p>If questioned visibly, the proprietor dismisses her by the next morning. If the party does not protect her, she vanishes from Greyhawk by the end of the phase.</p>",
        "public": ""
      },
